#==========================================================
# RATING & REVIEWS APIS
#==========================================================

### 1. Add a Review / Rating (Customer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/review/add
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entityId": "{{entityId}}",
  "entityModel": "Event",
  "rating": 5,
  "review": "Truly a spectacular event! High-quality organization and great atmosphere."
}

### 2. Get Reviews list for an Event / Course
GET {{baseUrl}}/review/list?entityId={{entityId}}&entityModel=Event&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 3. Update an existing Review (Customer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/review/update/{{reviewId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4,
  "review": "It was great, but updating rating slightly to 4 stars."
}

### 4. Get Organizer's reviews list
GET {{baseUrl}}/review/organizer-list?organizerId={{organizerId}}&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 5. Get My Submitted Reviews list (Customer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/review/user-list?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 6. Delete a Review (Customer/Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/review/delete/{{reviewId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
